{"name":"Mind Meme (Mystic Disturbance)","type":"talent","img":"icons/svg/sun.svg","data":{"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>You can seed an idea inside someone&rsquo;s subconscious. How the idea is received by the target or converted to actions is beyond your control.</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FAILURE</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You fail to seed the idea. You suffer from a strong headache. For the next hour, any wits-related skills are at -1.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">LIMITED SUCCESS</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The idea has been inserted into the target&rsquo;s mind.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">CRITICAL SUCCESS</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-341ae38e-7fff-7589-dc13-b5accff2d1a5\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You not only have inserted the idea inside the target&rsquo;s mind, but it surfaces into the target's conscious mind.</p>","category":"mysticalpowers","cost":0,"groupConcept":"","hpBonus":0,"mpBonus":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"97bsJYOh4FMjEg26":3},"flags":{},"_id":"5Z9xF1mZPxxpNSK3"}
{"name":"Affect Mood (Mystic Disturbance)","type":"talent","img":"icons/svg/sun.svg","data":{"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>You can slightly alter a person&rsquo;s mood. You can only augment or reduce the intensity of the target&rsquo;s current mood.</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FAILURE</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The target&rsquo;s mood shifts in the opposite direction to what was intended.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">LIMITED SUCCESS</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The target mood shifts in the intended direction.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">CRITICAL SUCCESS</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-011ed7a3-7fff-4315-f1e0-f47d8a6864bd\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The target&rsquo;s mood as well as those of others within close range also shift in the intended direction.</p>","category":"mysticalpowers","cost":0,"groupConcept":"agents","hpBonus":0,"mpBonus":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"97bsJYOh4FMjEg26":3},"flags":{},"_id":"JRx6F7wUF3GZvwgu"}
{"name":"Detect Spirits (Mystic Disturbance)","type":"talent","img":"icons/svg/sun.svg","data":{"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>You can detect if someone is possessed by a spirit or if a spirit is within short range.</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FAILURE</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The GM gives you false or misleading information.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">LIMITED SUCCESS</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The GM confirms whether a spirit is present.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">CRITICAL SUCCESS</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-71395628-7fff-911d-858a-3d27d23e028b\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If present, you can also sense the nature of the spirit, its general location,&nbsp; but not its intentions.</p>","category":"mysticalpowers","cost":0,"groupConcept":"","hpBonus":0,"mpBonus":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"97bsJYOh4FMjEg26":3},"flags":{},"_id":"NLIaQBZfrqDboMaJ"}
{"name":"Sense Mystic Powers (Mystic Disturbance)","type":"talent","img":"icons/svg/sun.svg","data":{"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>You can sense if someone has mystic powers.</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FAILURE</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The GM gives you false or misleading information. The target instinctively feels your presence.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">LIMITED SUCCESS</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The GM confirms whether the target has at least one skill point in MYSTIC POWERS.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">CRITICAL SUCCESS</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-46e37195-7fff-38aa-1b57-389f753335f6\">The GM provides information regarding how the target&rsquo;s skill level in MYSTIC POWERS compares to yours (lower, similar, higher).</span></p>","category":"mysticalpowers","cost":0,"groupConcept":"agents","hpBonus":0,"mpBonus":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"97bsJYOh4FMjEg26":3},"flags":{},"_id":"amipfSuFjVvzkGkE"}
{"name":"Detect Mania (Mystic Disturbance)","type":"talent","img":"icons/svg/sun.svg","data":{"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>You can feel when the Darkness Between the Stars affects people around you. This requires 5 minutes of concentration.</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FAILURE</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Your mind fills with doubts and fear. You suffer from 1 stress point.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">LIMITED SUCCESS</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You sense whether or not a person in close range is affected by a mania (core book p.337).</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">CRITICAL SUCCESS</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-84ac5c41-7fff-2e84-aa17-74e455efb92c\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You have an idea of the origin of the mania and how the mania is affecting the person.</p>","category":"mysticalpowers","cost":0,"groupConcept":"agents","hpBonus":0,"mpBonus":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"97bsJYOh4FMjEg26":3},"flags":{},"_id":"led2SgXvLd5I4CP5"}
{"name":"Read Artefacts (Mystic Disturbance)","type":"talent","img":"icons/svg/sun.svg","data":{"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>You can sense if an artefact has powers. This requires 15 minutes of concentration.</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FAILURE</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The GM gives you false or misleading information.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">LIMITED SUCCESS</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The GM confirms whether or not the artefact has powers.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">CRITICAL SUCCESS</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-867b841e-7fff-2760-d039-aefad6326f0f\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If the artefact has powers, the GM provides a general feeling of whether the powers are good or evil and a general indication of its power level.</p>","category":"mysticalpowers","cost":0,"groupConcept":"agents","hpBonus":0,"mpBonus":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"97bsJYOh4FMjEg26":3},"flags":{},"_id":"rnx4VmCCJEPllTno"}
{"name":"Survey Emotions (Mystic Disturbance)","type":"talent","img":"icons/svg/sun.svg","data":{"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>You can sense a person&rsquo;s emotions.</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FAILURE</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You are confused by a surge of different emotions. The GM gives you false or misleading information.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">LIMITED SUCCESS</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The GM tells you the current dominant emotion affecting the target.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">CRITICAL SUCCESS</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-40dffa00-7fff-5543-1b6f-34544198a703\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You can read an additional secondary emotion affecting the target.</p>","category":"mysticalpowers","cost":0,"groupConcept":"","hpBonus":0,"mpBonus":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"97bsJYOh4FMjEg26":3},"flags":{},"_id":"yv0IgcPIHLKMZUO9"}
